{
  "texts": [
    "The Project ID should be set to conspiracy_with_ai and the system message left empty.",
    "These values can be updated later through the Simple Chat dashboard.",
    "Notably, Costello et al. (2024) had LLMs create summaries of participants' conspiracy theory descriptions.",
    "Prior to the conversation with the LLM, participants were first asked whether they believed in any conspiracy theory and, if so, to specify which one.",
    "They were also asked to provide details about why they found the respective theory compelling, such as particular pieces of evidence."
  ]
}